Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧地 抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 刚才真是对不起 说得稍微过火了点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放在心上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没情调
